long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is a browser extension that makes it easier to view the official Vue.js documentation.
The Vue.js documentation is very clear, but there is no link from Version 2 to Version 3.
With this browser extension, you can get to the Version 3 page in one shot!
